on schedule, too.

49
00:03:25.650 --> 00:03:29.600
Now we just need to swap out the 
hentai scenes for cute ones!

50
00:03:29.600 --> 00:03:32.160
Like adding steam to hide the naughty bits,

51
00:03:32.160 --> 00:03:34.610
