52
00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:39.390
It may be a port, but it's best 
that we handle the CGs ourselves!

53
00:03:39.390 --> 00:03:41.980
Kao-san, you're really pulling 
out all the stops here!

54
00:03:41.980 --> 00:03:44.020
That goes without saying!

55
00:03:44.020 --> 00:03:46.510
A bishojo game lives and dies by its art!

56
00:03:46.510 --> 00:03:49.400
An eroge with no ero, huh?

57
00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:51.420
Call it a bishojo game!

58
00:03:51.420 --> 00:03:53.670
Oh, look at the time!

59
00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:57.990
Okay, Mei-chan and I have 
a meeting to attend!

60
00:03:57.990 --> 00:04:00.380
Take care now!

61
00:04:00.380 --> 00:04:04.020
When did this place turn 
into such a chick fest?

