Stay on the lookout for him

125
00:06:42.380 --> 00:06:44.510
Stay on the lookout for him.

126
00:06:52.420 --> 00:06:54.430
<i>What's up with that kid?</i>

127
00:06:54.430 --> 00:06:56.340
<i>He looks like he needs help.</i>

128
00:06:56.340 --> 00:06:58.880
<i>But right now, I'm in the 
middle of a stakeout!</i>

129
00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:03.400
<i>Mamoru even told me, "Don't 
do anything unnecessary!"</i>

130
00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:07.840
What's wrong?

131
00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:13.710
My coin rolled under the vending 
machine, and now I can't reach it...

132
00:07:13.710 --> 00:07:15.410
Dang...

133
00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:19.800
Do you mind if I borrow that?

134
00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:24.170
Use this like that and...

135
00:07:24.170 --> 00:07:25.740
There, got it!

136
00:07:26.870 --> 00:07:28.800
Thanks, lady!

137
00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:30.480
Bye-bye!

138
00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:30.930
Yeah!

139
00:07:33.330 --> 00:07:34.090
Ah!

140
00:07:34.090 --> 00:07:34.970
My mission!

141
00:07:35.550 --> 00:07:36.740
Onee-sama?

142
00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.440
It's you!

143
00:07:40.020 --> 00:07:41.690
Onee-sama!

144
00:07:41.690 --> 00:07:43.900
O-O-Onee-sama?!

145
00:07:43.900 --> 00:07:46.070
Do you remember me?

146
00:07:46.070 --> 00:07:49.400
You helped me buy <i>Pia Carrot</i> and <i>Kizuato</i>!

147
00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:50.060
Huh?

148
00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:55.330
Toya-chan?!

149
00:07:55.330 --> 00:07:56.780
That's right!

150
00:07:57.500 --> 00:08:00.050
You look way different from back then!

151
00:08:00.050 --> 00:08:02.300
A total redesign!

152
00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:06.290
I actually work for a game studio now!

153
00:08:06.290 --> 00:08:08.000
We're making an eroge!

154
00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.300
What?!

155
00:08:09.300 --> 00:08:13.200
I was tabling for a circle at Comiket, 
and they invited me to do lineart work.

156
00:08:13.200 --> 00:08:15.010
Now I'm a lead illustrator!

157
00:08:15.010 --> 00:08:17.260
What? That's amazing!

158
00:08:17.260 --> 00:08:19.710
I'm on my way to an event for our new title,

159
00:08:19.710 --> 00:08:23.010
which is why I'm dressed in this cosplay.

160
00:08:23.010 --> 00:08:25.280
The artist herself, promoting the game!

161
00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:28.900
The game I made is really popular!

162
00:08:28.900 --> 00:08:29.730
What?!

163
00:08:29.730 --> 00:08:32.060
That's great, Toya-chan!

164
00:08:32.060 --> 00:08:35.380
It's all thanks to you, Onee-sama.

165
00:08:35.380 --> 00:08:37.810
Huh? Did I do anything?

166
00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:38.370
Yes!

167
00:08:38.370 --> 00:08:40.500
You did so much for me!

168
00:08:40.740 --> 00:08:44.870
When we met, you talked about 
the future of bishojo games.

169
00:08:45.300 --> 00:08:47.990
Hearing that gave me the 
confidence I needed!

170
00:08:47.990 --> 00:08:49.990
That maybe I could do it, too!

171
00:08:50.260 --> 00:08:55.620
You were also the one who encouraged 
me to participate in Comiket.

172
00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:58.770
I really can't thank you enough!

173
00:09:02.710 --> 00:09:05.000
I used to just be a plain-looking otaku,

174
00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:07.850
but now I get treated like a princess.

175
00:09:07.850 --> 00:09:10.700
I didn't think it'd be so easy.

176
00:09:10.700 --> 00:09:11.390
Huh?

177
00:09:11.860 --> 00:09:14.940
Men are such simple creatures.

178
00:09:20.140 --> 00:09:21.790
Oh yeah, Onee-sama.

179
00:09:21.790 --> 00:09:23.710
Are you free after this?

180
00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:27.090
Would you care to join me 
for dinner after the event?

181
00:09:27.090 --> 00:09:29.470
There's this one café that I really like,

182
00:09:29.470 --> 00:09:30.850
<i>It's the manager!</i>

183
00:09:30.290 --> 00:09:31.980
and I'd love to catch up—

184
00:09:31.350 --> 00:09:33.800
I-I'm a little busy right now!

185
00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:35.740
See you around, Toya-chan!

186
00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:36.550
What?

187
00:09:39.140 --> 00:09:40.600
Onee-sama...

188
00:09:41.560 --> 00:09:42.650
Mamoru-kun!

189
00:09:42.650 --> 00:09:44.330
The manager's here!

190
00:09:44.330 --> 00:09:45.440
Go after him!

191
00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:45.940
What?!

192
00:09:45.940 --> 00:09:47.470
You want me to go in?!

193
00:09:47.470 --> 00:09:48.450
That's right!

194
00:09:48.450 --> 00:09:51.150
I don't wanna go in a place like that...

195
00:09:51.150 --> 00:09:52.180
Shut up and get going!

196
00:09:52.180 --> 00:09:53.450
That's an order!

197
00:09:53.450 --> 00:09:55.440
R-Roger...

198
00:09:58.780 --> 00:10:02.320
No one plays with Tamagotchi anymore.

199
00:10:02.320 --> 00:10:04.120
Don't be like that!

200
00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:07.360
You were so happy when
I gave you one the other day!

201
00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:09.920
It's totally out of fashion now.

202
00:10:10.490 --> 00:10:13.680
Is it any fun for a girl, 
coming to a club like this?

203
00:10:13.680 --> 00:10:15.150
Whoa, check it out!

204
00:10:15.150 --> 00:10:16.660
What's up with this hair?

205
00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.520
You dyed it blue on the inside?

206
00:10:18.520 --> 00:10:19.500
Shh!

207
00:10:19.500 --> 00:10:21.510
Please be quiet!

208
00:10:22.270 --> 00:10:25.110
Buy me an Aibo instead!

209
00:10:25.110 --> 00:10:26.960
That thing's <i>so</i> cute!

210
00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.710
Hey now, girls!

211
00:10:28.710 --> 00:10:31.070
I'm the owner of this joint, you know!

212
00:10:31.330 --> 00:10:34.530
You've got some nerve talking 
to the owner like that!

213
00:10:34.530 --> 00:10:35.810
The owner?

214
00:10:35.810 --> 00:10:39.800
You should be a little nicer to me!

215
00:10:39.800 --> 00:10:43.000
I'm about to become a big shot real soon!

216
00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:44.130
For real?

217
00:10:44.130 --> 00:10:47.790
Well, I bet you wouldn't get it, anyway!

218
00:10:47.790 --> 00:10:51.190
Kaori and Meiko should 
be thanking me, dammit!

219
00:10:51.190 --> 00:10:56.010
They're always looking down on me for 
not knowing jack about video games!

220
00:10:56.010 --> 00:10:59.050
Talking real big for a bunch of artists!

221
00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:01.950
I don't get it, but that's wack.

222
00:11:02.400 --> 00:11:03.480
Just you wait!

223
00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:06.860
Ichigaya and I are gonna take the 
video game industry by storm!

224
00:11:06.860 --> 00:11:10.750
<i>I'm</i> the one who managed 
to land the console deal!

225
00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:11.940
They don't know...

226
00:11:11.940 --> 00:11:14.690
how much money I've invested 
to make that happen!

227
00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.700
<i>Invested?!</i>

228
00:11:17.140 --> 00:11:18.600
Screw the artists!

229
00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:21.130
The president deserves the most credit!

230
00:11:27.250 --> 00:11:28.810
Good job, prez!

231
00:11:27.470 --> 00:11:29.680
I need to let Mamoru know!

232
00:11:28.810 --> 00:11:30.360
Wait, that's me!

233
00:11:30.360 --> 00:11:31.670
Good job, me!

