240
00:11:48.270 --> 00:11:49.600
Screw the artists!

241
00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:52.140
The president deserves the most credit!

242
00:11:55.270 --> 00:11:57.270
What the hell is this?

243
00:11:57.270 --> 00:11:59.860
Am I the one who said that?

244
00:11:59.860 --> 00:12:02.440
I was drunk, so I don't remember.

245
00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:03.750
Manager...

246
00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:05.970
